The '''Three Peaks of Tharen''' was a mountain range on the planet [[Kalarba/Legends|Kalarba]] near the immense equatorial zone. The local Kalarbans believed that their great spirit of strength was embodied within the mountains. It overlooked the nearby [[Great Sea (Kalarba)|Great Sea]] and the planetary capital [[Kalarba City]] and Kalarba City Spaceport.

